Titolo: Horrible Histories: Ruthless Romans (video game)

Anno: 2009

Descrizione: Horrible Histories: Ruthless Romans, is a 2009 educational adventure video game theme on Ancient Rome as part of the Horrible Histories franchise, which began in 1993. The game was released on Wii, Nintendo DS and Windows and is narrated by Terry Deary, the author of the Horrible Histories book series. It is named after Deary's 2003 book Ruthless Romans, his second on the topic after 1999's Rotten Romans.